    title: 'How to keep the spark alive after many years',
    contentOn: 'A spark doesn\'t stay on its own after many years - it requires attention. Routine, children, work - it\'s easy to forget about it.\n\nPlan moments just for you. Dating, trips, new experiences. Not "when it\'s time" - in the calendar.\n\nSurprise. Little surprises, compliments, initiative. Your partner will appreciate that you are still trying.\n\nA spark isn\'t just passion - it\'s curiosity about the other person. Ask, listen, discover. People change - get to know her anew.',
