    contentOna: 'A shared vision of the future is the compass of relationships. Where are you going? Without answers, it\'s easy to drift apart.\n\nTalk about dreams. Home, family, career, travel - what do you want to build together?\n\nLook for a common direction. You don\'t have to agree on everything - just some overlapping visions.\n\nReview the vision from time to time. Lives change - open conversation keeps you as a team with a common goal.',
